s been in continuous use since the Middle Ages."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Pierre de Montoire II was born in 1145, in Paris, Île-de-France, France, his father, Philippe de Montoire, was 20 and his mother, Létitia de Savonnières, was 17. He married Agnes Preuilly de Vendôme in 1174, in Vendôme, Loir-et-Cher, France. They were the parents of at least 1 son and 1 daughter. He died in 1201, at the age of 56."},"et":{"1145–1201":"1145–1201","1150–1201":"1150–1201","1175–1240":"1175–1240","1180–1230":"1180–1230","1125–1207":"1125–1207","1128–1207":"1128–1207","1128":"1128","1125":"1125","1201":"1201","1145":"1145","1230":"1230","1175":"1175","1174":"1174","1240":"1240","1150":"1150","about 1175":"umbes 1175","1180":"1180","1207":"1207","Vendôme, Loir-et-Cher, Centre-Val de Loire, France":"Vendôme, Loir-et-Cher, Prantsusmaa","Montoire, Loiret, Centre-Val de Loire, France":"Montoire, Loiret, Centre, Prantsusmaa","Vendôme, Loir-et-Cher, Centre, France":"Vendôme, Loir-et-Cher, Prantsusmaa","Maillé, Chinon, Indre-et-Loire, Centre-Val de Loire, France":"Maillé, Indre-et-Loire, Centre, Prantsusmaa","Paris, Île-de-France, France":"Paris, Île-de-France, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1145–1201":"1145–1201","1150–1201":"1150–1201","1175–1240":"1175–1240","1180–1230":"1180–1230","1125–1207":"1125–1207","1128–1207":"1128–1207","1128":"1128","1125":"1125","1201":"1201","1145":"1145","1230":"1230","1175":"1175","1174":"1174","1240":"1240","1150":"1150","about 1175":"noin 1175","1180":"1180","1207":"1207","Vendôme, Loir-et-Cher, Centre-Val de Loire, France":"Vendôme, Loir-et-Cher, Ranska","Montoire, Loiret, Centre-Val de Loire, France":"Montoire, Loiret, Centre, Ranska","Vendôme, Loir-et-Cher, Centre, France":"Vendôme, Loir-et-Cher, Ranska","Maillé, Chinon, Indre-et-Loire, Centre-Val de Loire, France":"Maillé, Indre-et-Loire, Centre, Ranska","Paris, Île-de-France, France":"Paris, Île-de-France, Ranska"},"fr":{"1145–1201":"1145–1201","1150–1201":"1150–1201","1175–1240":"1175–1240","1180–1230":"1180